      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "Used car in poor condition. It runs and drives, but it has noticeable wear, cosmetic damage, and clear signs of age and use throughout. The interior and exterior are both rough overall, and it will likely need repairs and maintenance soon. Best suited for someone looking for basic transportation or a project vehicle.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "Runs and drives, but this is a fair-condition used car with noticeable cosmetic wear and signs of age. It should work as basic transportation, but it is not a clean or like-new example. Expect imperfections inside and out and plan on the kind of upkeep that comes with an older, average-used vehicle.",
      "price": 19800.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Clean, good-condition vehicle that has been well kept and should make a solid daily driver or comfortable all-around car. It shows well overall with a nice appearance inside and out, though you should still expect normal signs of use such as minor cosmetic wear, light blemishes, and age-appropriate wear on interior surfaces and exterior trim. Nothing about it is presented as perfect, but it is a strong, honest example that feels cared for and much nicer than a fair-condition car.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Well-kept good-condition example that should make a solid choice for someone wanting a clean, usable car without paying top-dollar for a showpiece. The exterior should present nicely overall with a respectable shine, straight-looking body, and trim that shows normal age rather than major neglect. Inside, expect a clean and serviceable cabin with typical wear in the commonly used areas, but nothing suggesting it has been abused. Overall, buyers should expect an honest, above-average driver that has been cared for, with some normal cosmetic and age-related imperfections if you look closely.",
      "price": 32900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Dependable transportation at an affordable price. This vehicle shows its age but remains a practical choice for buyers seeking a straightforward, budget-conscious option. A solid value for commuting, first-time drivers, or anyone needing an inexpensive extra vehicle, it offers honest utility and the confidence of a transparent sale from a trusted seller.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car looking for its next home. It\u2019s not perfect, but it still has plenty to offer for someone after affordable wheels, a handy runabout, or a tidy project to tinker with. A great chance to get into a car without spending a fortune, and I\u2019m happy to be upfront and easy to deal with. If you want something budget-friendly with potential, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver project with strong enthusiast upside. This car shows its age cosmetically and will want TLC, but it still presents as a complete, usable platform with good bones. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels straightforward and mechanical, and it offers the kind of analog driving character that\u2019s getting harder to find. A great candidate for someone who wants an affordable entry point, a weekend tinkering car, or a practical runabout they can improve over time. Priced to reflect condition while leaving plenty of room for the next owner to add value.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap, honest ride. Used and rough, but priced to move. Great budget beater or project. First serious buyer takes it.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Built for someone who sees potential, not just polish, this car has the kind of honest, road-worn character that turns errands into a story. It wears its years openly, but that is exactly where the charm lives: a practical ride for a budget-minded driver, a hands-on project for a tinkerer, or a dependable spare to keep around when having an extra set of keys matters. If you appreciate value, grit, and the chance to make something your own, this one has the right kind of presence.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation with solid value for the money. An ideal choice for a commuter, first-time driver, or buyer looking for an affordable project, it delivers practical utility at a hard-to-beat price point. If you want inexpensive entry into ownership without overpaying, this is a smart opportunity worth a look.",
      "price": 5495.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    }
  ],
